Class Memory

  • java.lang.Object
    • Memory

  • public class Memory
extends java.lang.Object
    Memory is used by the Bot. every time a card is player, it is sent to memory. The bot then uses what is in memory in certain situations to figure out which card should be played next.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors
